      <title>Verizon 希望从美国移动公司回购洛杉矶股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/verizon-wants-los-angeles-business-stake-back-from-us-cellular</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Verizon 消费者部门负责人表示，如果美国移动通信公司能够就合理价格达成一致，Verizon 有意回购其在洛杉矶业务的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/verizon-wants-los-angeles-business-stake-back-from-us-cellular</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:07:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将中国加密货币矿工赶出空军基地附近的土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/us-kicks-chinese-crypto-mining-firm-off-land-near-air-force-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国命令一家中国加密货币挖矿公司腾出并出售其在怀俄明州空军基地附近购买的一处房产，该基地装有洲际弹道导弹，称该公司对国家安全构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/us-kicks-chinese-crypto-mining-firm-off-land-near-air-force-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 20:22:35 GMT</pubDate>
